data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET, BUYER UNABLE TO OBTAIN FINANCING- FHA APPRAISAL ABOVE LIST AS WELL AS A SQUEAKY-CLEAN INSPECTION! This delightful three-bedroom home exudes a cheery ambiance from the moment you step inside. The entire house is immaculately clean and ready for you to move in, with fresh new carpet and beautiful wood flooring that gleams with warmth. The updated kitchen is a focal point, boasting an island that beckons for gatherings. Each bedroom is a cozy retreat, with the primary offering a large walk-in closet and 3/4 bath.  A cozy office space offers a perfect retreat for productivity and the electric fireplace adds warmth to the heart of the home. Don't miss this oversized three-car garage offering convenience and functionality, complete with a convenient pull-through feature. Outside, a spacious backyard promises endless joy and relaxation. Immaculately maintained and move-in ready, this home radiates warmth and comfort.
